Components:-
Arduino UNO x1
HX711 amplifier x1
5kg load cell x1
LCD display x1
Red LED x1
Buzzer x1


Connections:-
lcd to arduino
gnd (arduino) --> gnd (lcd)
5v (arduino) --> vcc (lcd)
A4 (arduino) --> sda (lcd)
A5 (arduino) --> scl (lcd)

hx711 to arduino
gnd (arduino) --> gnd (amp)
D4 (arduino) --> dt (amp)
D5 (arduino) --> sck (amp)
3.3v (arduino) --> vcc (amp)

load cell to amplifier
red --> E+
black --> E-
white  A-
green --> A+

led 
postive --> 10k ohms resister --> D7 (arduino)
negative --> gnd (arduino)[merged]

buzzer 
positive --> d8 (a)
negative --> gndÂ (arduino)[merged]
